* Frank Medrano as &#x27;Fat&#x27; Mancho
* Eugene Byrd as Rizzo Robinson
* Jeffrey Donovan as Henry Addison
* Wendell Pierce as Eddie &#x27;Little Caesar&#x27; Robinson
