*Field hockey - AAA
*Lacrosse - AAA
*Soccer - AAA
*Softball - AAAA
*Tennis - AAA
*Track and field - AAA
*Volleyball - AAA
;Middle school sports:
;Boys:
*Basketball
*Cross country
*Football
